<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Centos on CornRadio-Blog</title><link>https://b.cornradio.org/tags/centos/</link><description>Recent content in Centos on CornRadio-Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 14 Feb 2022 09:56:15 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://b.cornradio.org/tags/centos/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Permission Denied (publickey,gssapi-keyex,gssapi-with-mic) 解决办法</title><link>https://b.cornradio.org/p/permission-denied-publickeygssapi-keyexgssapi-with-mic-%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Mon, 14 Feb 2022 09:56:15 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://b.cornradio.org/p/permission-denied-publickeygssapi-keyexgssapi-with-mic-%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>&lt;p>今天ssh登录阿里云远程的centos，出现了&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Permission denied (publickey,gssapi-keyex,gssapi-with-mic)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>尝试使用生成的key（pem文件）没有成功。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ssh -i myvmubuntu.pem root@123.56.18.36
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>提示如下错误：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Permission denied (publickey,gssapi-keyex,gssapi-with-mic)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h1 id="解决方案">解决方案
&lt;/h1>&lt;p>修改这文件:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>搜索如下两项：并把后面修改成如下所示&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">PasswordAuthentication yes
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">……
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>重启sshd：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo systemctl restart sshd
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>